org.gearvrf.physics

Class GVRPoint2PointConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • GVRComponent
      • org.gearvrf.physics.GVRPoint2PointConstraint

  • public class GVRPoint2PointConstraint
extends GVRComponent
    Represents a constraint that restricts translation of two rigid bodies to keep fixed distance from a local pivot.

        Constructs new instance of point-to-point constraint.
        Parameters:
        gvrContext - the context of the app
        rigidBodyB - the second rigid body (not the owner) in this constraint
        pivotInA - the pivot point (x, y and z coordinates) related to body A (the owner)
        pivotInB - the pivot point related to body B
